                                    <li class="slide xlarge-25 large-25 medium-33 small-50 tiny-100">
                    <a href="/mundo/miguel_diaz-canel_recebe_felicitacoes#foto">                                    
                                                    <img src="http://thumbs.web.sapo.io/?pic=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.sapo.pt%2Fjornaldeangola%2Fimg%2Fthumb1%2F20180420070526diaz.jpg&W=304&H=163&errorpic=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.sapo.pt%2Fjornaldeangola%2F2016%2F%2Fimg%2Fdefault-article-2017.png" alt="">
                        
                        <div class="description">
                            <h4 class="no-margin">Miguel D&iacute;az-Canel recebe felicita&ccedil;&otilde;es</h4>
                        </div>
